### QueueCure Backend Test Cases (REST Client / VSCode)

@auth_service = http://localhost:3002
@hospital_service = http://localhost:3001
@queue_service = http://localhost:3003
@triage_service = http://localhost:3004

### 1. Auth Service: Login (Patient)
POST {{auth_service}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "patient",
  "phone": "+919876543210"
}

### 2. Hospital Service: Get Hospitals
GET {{hospital_service}}/hospitals?city=Mumbai&specialty=Cardiology
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Triage Service: Symptom Analysis (AI Triage)
POST {{triage_service}}/triage
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient_id": "p-1234",
  "symptoms": "Severe chest pain radiating to left arm, shortness of breath, sweating.",
  "duration": "30 mins"
}

### 4. Queue Service: Generate Walk-in Token
POST {{queue_service}}/tokens
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hospital_id": "hosp-1",
  "doctor_id": "doc-sharma-1",
  "patient_name": "Raj Kumar",
  "source": "walk_in",
  "priority": "normal"
}

### 5. Queue Service: Generate Emergency Token (After Triage)
POST {{queue_service}}/tokens
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hospital_id": "hosp-1",
  "doctor_id": "doc-sharma-1",
  "patient_name": "Amit Singh",
  "source": "online",
  "priority": "urgent"
}

### 6. Queue Service: Call Next Patient (Receptionist)
POST {{queue_service}}/queue/call-next
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doctor_id": "doc-sharma-1",
  "receptionist_id": "rec-01"
}

### 7. Queue Service: SSE Stream Subscription (Open in browser or curl)
# curl -N "http://localhost:3003/queue/stream?doctorId=doc-sharma-1"
GET {{queue_service}}/queue/stream?doctorId=doc-sharma-1
Accept: text/event-stream

### 8. Queue Service: AI Hospital Switch Suggestion
POST {{queue_service}}/tokens/switch-suggest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token_id": "token-1234",
  "current_wait_time": 120,
  "max_radius_km": 5
}
